Recommends: apache2,
             skywarnplus-ng-voice-en-us-amy-low (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Weather alert system for Asterisk/app_rpt nodes
 SkywarnPlus-NG polls NWS alerts, drives voice announcements on Asterisk
 nodes, and provides a web dashboard. This package ships a prebuilt Python
 virtualenv so nodes do not download dependencies with pip at install time.
 .
 Target systems are AllStar Link 3 nodes with asl3-asterisk already installed.

Package: skywarnplus-ng-voice-en-us-amy-low
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: skywarnplus-ng (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Piper en_US-amy-low voice for SkywarnPlus-NG
 Optional voice model files for local Piper TTS (default SkywarnPlus-NG voice).

Package: skywarnplus-ng-all
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: skywarnplus-ng (= ${binary:Version}),
         skywarnplus-ng-voice-en-us-amy-low (= ${binary:Version})
Section: metapackages
Description: SkywarnPlus-NG with default Piper voice (metapackage)
 Installs skywarnplus-ng and the recommended en_US-amy-low Piper voice model.
